CASE ANNOUNCEMENTS

March 26, 2008

[Cite as 03/26/2008 Case Announcements, 2008-0hio-1279.]

MERIT DECISIONS WITHOUT OPINIONS

2008-0080. State ex rel. Brown v. Rogers.

In Mandamus. On respondents’ motion to dismiss and relator’s amended motion for stay. Motion to dismiss granted. Motion for stay denied. Cause dismissed.

Moyer, C.J., and Pfeifer, Lundberg Stratton, O’Connor, O’Donnell, and Lanzinger, JJ., concur. Cupp, J., not participating.
